reviews.text: One of the most impressive dim sum restaurants recently. Every dish was impeccable, so as to the service. My daughter lost her toy ring on the table, the waitress kept it carefully and gave it back to us right upon we were back to the restaurant to search for it! Will definitely visit again and recommend to all my friends!
Pigeon and sweet and sour pork is a must here.  Really enjoyed all the dishes we ordered and service was good. Would recommend

Social Place is a great place for anybody. They server food that are cute at times like the piggy bums or dare yourself to try the roasted pigeon! It can be busy at all times but the best time is during the weekends for lunch or late evening dinner. It is within the L Place.

Each piece of dishes are very delicious.  This restaurant’s signature dish baked pigeon is more distinctive than chickens and are delicious with rich oil.  We ate pigeon to wears gloves and attack it wildly. I also recommend delicious Chimaki. It is needed to wait standing in line over 30min without reservations.

The food is excellent and the service is quick.  Their menu changes from time to time and the presentation of the food is quite creative. It’s upstairs — the name on the building outside, at street level, is “the L. place”.  Great place for a good and quick lunch with friends.

result.name: 唐宮小聚

reviews.text: 中環錯之食飯地點

已經有一段時間沒有來這家飲茶了🤔
去到的時候是剛剛開門不久 所以沒太多人
可以隨心而選擇位置坐 這樣挻不錯耶🤭

·金獎乳鴿
每一次來到我也會必點這個 味道很棒棒噠
外皮造到鬆脆可口 而且肉質鮮嫰挻Juicy
一人半隻也不錯耶~Happy Share才食到更多

·金牌蘿蔔糕 
用鐵板放著蘿蔔糕除了賣相 還可以保溫外 
也可以令醬汁不會粘在一起🤤
外皮也是脆脆的 蘿蔔糕挻煙韌 味道挻香的
不過要趁熱食才可以保持口感 放涼了不好食

·棋子流沙包 
流沙包有誰不愛? 到酒樓怎樣可不點這個食[加油]
裡面流心的奶黃雖然很邪惡 但又很想食🤤🤤

·沙薑豬手 
這個味道的豬手是第一次食 醬汁是不錯的
可惜的是咸了一點 醬汁是否放多了醬油[笑哭]
但豬手是很腍身挻易咬開的 而且有豐富骨膠原

·辣口水雞 
第二次食這個 雞皮和雞肉很容易分開😉
不想食也很容易撕開 雞肉挻滑身的
雞件不會太辣 很快就被我們食光光[笑哭]

CP值挻高的一餐 價錢也不會太貴
到了飯市已經要等位🤔 幸好我喜歡早上去[愉快]

One of the most impressive dim sum restaurants recently. Every dish was impeccable, so as to the service. My daughter lost her toy ring on the table, the waitress kept it carefully and gave it back to us right upon we were back to the restaurant to search for it! Will definitely visit again and recommend to all my friends!

非常好吃，每道菜不管是視覺還是口味都相當驚艷。環境舒適，服務也很到位，上菜速度剛剛好，價格亦相當合理。

令人感動的是，離開二十分鐘之後發現女兒心愛的玩具戒指掉了，返回詢問店員，立刻就幫忙找回來，非常有同理心，真心感謝，推薦👍
Pigeon and sweet and sour pork is a must here.  Really enjoyed all the dishes we ordered and service was good. Would recommend

result.name: Citywalk

reviews.text: Huge shopping mall with lots of outlets and plenty of things to do. Worth a visit if you are relaxing in Tsuen Wan and just want some place to kill time, or if you're out to shop till you drop and come home with a haul. Food options are also plenty, but nothing novel - look at it as refueling opportunities rather than experiences.
Nice mall where you can spend a day for shopping and eating
Fully car parking. No good restaurant. Forget this mall and never come again
An pretty good shopping mall in a convenient location in Tsuen Wan, interconnected with other major malls in the area.
Spacious with a bunch of mid-range shops. Some great eateries there too. Overall a cheerful place.
